  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hot and cold buffet breakfast with selection of regional products, fresh fruits and yoghurts, vital corner and juice bar. </p>
<p>You evening meal is four courses plus a salad buffet. Enjoyment and the environment are both important for the team at the Berghof and they value local produce in their creation of delicious local and national food. When the weather's nice, you can dine al fresco.</p>
<p><strong>The Bar and Wine Cellar </strong>has a large collection of national and international wines. A cosy lounge, welcoming atmosphere and regular live music in the garden make it a lovely spot for an afternoon or evening drink. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
