  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Berghof is just a few hundred metres from the train station and main street in central <a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a> so getting around is easy. Public areas are recently refurbished and rooms are spacious and neatly furnished.</p>
<h2>Great family facilities and activities</h2>
<p>The hotel has tennis and squash courts, free use of hotel's bikes and fantastic children's facilities including a children's pool, outdoor play park and indoor games room.</p>
<p>For those after a more relaxing break, there's a recently renovated spa and wellness area including indoor/outdoor pool, saunas and stunning relaxation areas, plus yoga and fitness room.</p>
<h2>Evenings of excellent food, wine and music</h2>
<p>Enjoy culinary variety throughout the week, delivered with a personal level of service in the homely restaurant. Emphasis on enjoyment and sustainability means great food made with local produce, and daily live music from mid-June to September adds to your experience. Head to the elegant bar and lounge area to try a glass of wine from their extensive national and international wine cellar. </p>]]></description>
