  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h4><strong>Guided walks with Zillertal Natur Programme</strong></h4>
<p>The Berghof is a partner of the Zillertal Natur Programme which runs a programme of guided walks from the end of May. Sign up via reception to take part.</p>
<h4><strong>Hotel facilities:</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>Brand new spacious wellness area with indoor/outdoor pool, baby and children's pool and family sauna</li>
<li>Sauna world with two Finnish saunas, herbal sauna, steam room, infrared lounge and relaxation areas</li>
<li>Rooftop sunbathing area (adults only)</li>
<li>Garden with sun loungers</li>
<li>Yoga room and gym</li>
<li>Indoor and outdoor tennis courts</li>
<li>Squash court</li>
<li>Massage and solarium (payable locally)</li>
<li>Billiards and games room with pinball machines and table football</li>
<li>Free use of hotel's bikes (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Dogs are accepted for €20 per day (without food or basket)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Baby/children's pool</li>
<li>Outdoor play park with swings, slide and climbing frame</li>
<li>Playroom with Lego and games corner</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
