<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>10pm</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2.20 per person per night is payable locally. Children under the age of 15yrs are exempt. </p>
